## Common Runtime Errors -> Causes

| Error / Symptom | Likely Cause | Fix |
|----------------|-------------|-----|
| Custom error `SenderNotAllowed(address)` (`ACL.sol:106`) | Missing `FHE.allow()` for the caller, or transient ACL expired because `FHE.allowThis()` was missing | Add `FHE.allow(value, msg.sender)` and/or `FHE.allowThis(value)` |
| Custom error `ACLNotAllowed(bytes32, address)` (`FHEVMExecutor.sol:37`) | FHE op tried to read a handle the calling contract has no ACL on | Trace the missing `FHE.allowThis(handle)` step |
| Custom error `SenderNotAllowedToUseHandle(bytes32, address)` (`FHE.sol:74 declaration; FHE.sol:8502 revert site`) | `FHE.fromExternal` Path 2 (no proof) on a handle the contract has no ACL on | Pass the original `inputProof` or grant transient ACL first |
| Compile error `Member "div" not found ...` | Encrypted divisor passed to `FHE.div`/`FHE.rem` (no overload) | Restructure so the divisor is `uintN` plaintext |
| Custom error `DivisionByZero()` (`FHEVMExecutor.sol:40`) | `FHE.div(x, 0)` or `FHE.rem(x, 0)` | Guard the plaintext divisor: `require(divisor != 0)` |
| Custom error `NotPowerOfTwo()` (`FHEVMExecutor.sol:55`) | `FHE.randEuintX(upperBound)` with non-power-of-2 bound | Use a power-of-2 upperBound |
| Custom error `KMSInvalidSigner(address)` (`KMSVerifier.sol:22`) OR `InvalidKMSSignatures()` (`FHE.sol:71 declaration; FHE.sol:9502 revert site`) | `FHE.checkSignatures` got cts/cleartexts in wrong order vs `publicDecrypt`, or KMS sig set below threshold. Runtime usually surfaces `KMSInvalidSigner` first (recovered address rejected); `InvalidKMSSignatures` is the FHE-library wrapper raised when `_verifySignatures` returns false. | Reorder cts/cleartexts to match the off-chain `publicDecrypt` exactly |
| `EmptyInputProof` / `DeserializingInputProofFail` / `InvalidInputHandle` (`InputVerifier.sol`) | Wrong / stale `inputProof` paired with handle | Use `inputProof` from the same `instance.createEncryptedInput(...).encrypt()` call |
| `EmptyDecryptionProof` / `DeserializingDecryptionProofFail` (`KMSVerifier.sol`) | `FHE.checkSignatures` received empty / malformed `decryptionProof` | Pass the raw `results.decryptionProof` from the relayer SDK |
| Custom error `ZamaProtocolUnsupported()` (`ZamaConfig.sol:15`) | Inheriting `ZamaEthereumConfig` and deploying to a chain other than 1 / 11155111 / 31337 | Deploy to a supported chain or write a custom config base |
| Custom error `HCUTransactionLimitExceeded()` / `HCUTransactionDepthLimitExceeded()` (`HCULimit.sol:22, 25`) | A single tx exceeded `MAX_HOMOMORPHIC_COMPUTE_UNITS_PER_TX = 20_000_000` total HCU or `MAX_HOMOMORPHIC_COMPUTE_UNITS_DEPTH_PER_TX = 5_000_000` sequential-depth HCU | Split work across txs, prefer `euint64`, budget with `fhevm.computeTransactionHCU(receipt)` |
| Compile error "function not found" on FHE | Wrong function name (`neq`, `lte`, `TFHE.`) | Check exact name in operations table |

